Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "pip install llmcast" Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "cd ~/my-rag-project" Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "llmcast init" Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# ... after a few days of building ..." Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "llmcast forecast" Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "llmcast forecast --brief" Enter
Sleep 2s
